This patient has been in prior studies with our group and he has really not shown signs of depressed mood in the past either.  He does have a sense of awareness of his deficits and rightly appraises the gravity of his illness on the GDS.  In prior studies with our group he has amyloid imaging (when he was MCI) and is strongly amyloid positive.
